Description: lintipy
        =======
        
        **Run python based static file linters on AWS lambda.**
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        .. code-block::python
        
            from lintipy import Handler
        
            handle = Handler('PEP8', 'pycodestyle', '.')
        
        
